### 5. 视觉分析 `agents/vision_analyzer.py`

```python
# 调用多模态 LLM（GPT-4o / Claude）分析帧图像

VISION_PROMPT = """
你是一个专业摄影助手，分析以下相机取景帧，识别存在的拍摄问题。

请从以下维度评估，只输出 JSON，不要任何解释：

{
  "lighting": {
    "issue": true/false,
    "detail": "过暗/过曝/逆光/正常",
    "severity": 1-3
  },
  "composition": {
    "issue": true/false,
    "detail": "主体偏左/主体偏右/主体居中（推荐三分法）/无明显主体",
    "severity": 1-3
  },
  "stability": {
    "issue": true/false,
    "detail": "画面模糊/轻微抖动/稳定",
    "severity": 1-3
  },
  "focus": {
    "issue": true/false,
    "detail": "对焦失准/对焦中/对焦准确",
    "severity": 1-3
  },
  "other": {
    "issue": true/false,
    "detail": "镜头脏污/玻璃反光/障碍物遮挡/无",
    "severity": 1-3
  }
}
"""

async def analyze(image: Image) -> VisionResult:
    response = await llm_client.chat(
        model="gpt-4o",
        messages=[
            {"role": "user", "content": [
                {"type": "image_url", "image_url": {"url": to_base64_url(image)}},
                {"type": "text", "text": VISION_PROMPT}
            ]}
        ]
    )
    return VisionResult.parse_raw(response.content)
```

